#: index.docbook:415 index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide the mouse cursor in the magnified image."
msgstr "Visa eller dölj muspekaren i den förstorade bilden."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stays On Top</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> <keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Inställningar</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stannar överst</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427 index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kmagnifier; window stays on top of other windows."
msgstr "Förstoringsglasets fönster förblir ovanpå övriga fönster."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kmagnifier; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Dessutom har Förstoringsglaset de vanliga menyalternativen "
"<guimenu>Inställningar</guimenu> och <guimenu>Hjälp</guimenu> i &kde;. För "
"mer information, läs avsnitten  <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-settings\">Menyn Inställningar</ulink> och <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Menyn Hjälp</ulink> i &kde;:s Grunder."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Kommandoreferens"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmagnifier; automatically uses all your default shortcuts for saving file, "
"opening new window, printing, starting/stopping refresh (reload button in "
"&konqueror;), zoom-in, zoom-out &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Förstoringsglaset använder automatiskt alla dina vanliga snabbtangenter för "
"att spara filer, öppna nya fönster, skriva ut, starta och stoppa "
"uppdateringar (uppdateringsknappen i &konqueror;), zooma in, zooma ut, etc."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Förvalda snabbtangenter"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will save the contents of the zoom window to a file."
msgstr "Det här sparar innehållet i zoomfönstret till en fil."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F2</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F2</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to \"Follow Mouse Mode\"."
msgstr "Byt till läget \"Följ musen\"."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F3</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F3</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to \"Selection Window Mode\"."
msgstr "Byt till läget \"Markeringsfönster\"."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F4</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F4</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to \"Whole Screen Mode\"."
msgstr "Byt till läget \"Hela skärmen\"."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F5</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F5</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will start the refresh of the zoom window if it is stopped, or stops "
"the refresh of the zoom window if the refresh is currently on."
msgstr ""
"Det här startar uppdatering av zoomfönstret om den är stoppad, eller stoppar "
"uppdateringen av zoomfönstret om den för närvarande är på."

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F6</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F6</keycap>"

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F7</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F7</keycap>"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will open a new &kmagnifier; window."
msgstr "Det här öppnar ett nytt förstoringsglasfönster."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will open the print dialog for printing the contents of the zoom window."
msgstr ""
"Det här öppnar utskriftsdialogrutan för att skriva ut innehållet i "
"zoomfönstret."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will copy the zoom window contents to the clipboard."
msgstr "Det här kopierar zoomfönstrets innehåll till klippbordet."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show/Hide the menubar."
msgstr "Visa/göm menyraden."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom out"
msgstr "Zooma ut"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom in"
msgstr "Zooma in"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quits the application."
msgstr "Avslutar programmet."

